Abstract = {Globally, Indigenous Peoples' dissent against unjust state and corporate
   incursions in their lands is being suppressed. States and corporations
   use penal laws, anti-terrorist legislation, and emergency powers to
   justify the detention of activists, who are subject to intimidation,
   human rights violations, or, at worst, extrajudicial killings. In 2019,
