   design and end-of-engineered-life management},
Journal = {RENEWABLE \& SUSTAINABLE ENERGY REVIEWS},
Year = {2022},
Volume = {154},
Month = {FEB},
Abstract = {Thousands of structures are currently installed in our oceans to help
