Month = {NOV},
Abstract = {Using data from two recently available living standards surveys, we
   trace the dynamics in cooking fuel choice among Ghanaian households over
   the period 2005/6 and 2012/13 and further investigate the main forces
   driving households' choice of a cooking fuel. Evidence from this paper
