   photophysical processes involved with different excitonic features in
   few layer WS2, modeled as a TMDC representative. We observed a strong
   intervalley coupling across the momentum space and proposed the most
   plausible relaxation pathway for different excitons in few layer
   scenario. C and D exciton dynamics were significantly slower as compared
